Imports:
  Rcpp (>= 1.1.1),
  hardhat (>= 1.4.0),
  checkmate (>= 2.1.0),
  testthat (>= 3.3.0),
  survival (>= 3.8)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Encoding: UTF-8
